/*
	This file contains all the macro EVENT_TYPE that will be used for declaring
	all the different event types. 

	Example of how it works
	EVENT_TYPE(Type of event, parameters for said event)

	Note: Do comment the type of parameters each event type will take so that when 
	you're going through EventType (an enum), you will be able to see the argument 
	type for each said event

	Note 2: All events only accept argument types, no return value
*/

// parameters => int
EVENT_TYPE(MouseInput, int)
// parameters => int, std::string const&
EVENT_TYPE(KeyboardInput, int, std::string const&)